{"tid":1909920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】高永文：口罩防疫功用無人講得準   鼓勵戴口罩是製造氣氛","createTime":"2020-03-04T09:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T17:24:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e13cf53a0e84964e7222ae2409591368b35f8e26","tid":1909920,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200304/s00001/6f8fc79ead29cb1191bf4a8cb89f33ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200304%2Fs00001%2F6f8fc79ead29cb1191bf4a8cb89f33ac.jpg&h=84cea4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎襲港，全國政協委員、食物及衛生局前局長高永文今日（4日）形容，香港、內地及澳門均實施史無前例及適當的防疫措施，有聆聽專家意見，他稱見到確診新增病例數目下降，但強調仍要防範，尤其對外地回港的人需嚴謹戒備。他稱，專家都認同政府措施，但強調不可鬆懈。<br />\n<br />\n被問到對「封關」的看法，他指出，應要看具體措施可減低多少人流，認為專家都接受現時的措施。<br />\n<br />\n高永文又稱，在疫情高峰期，鼓勵戴口罩是製造氣氛及提高警惕，以製造社交距離，但口罩防疫功用「無人講得準」，因戴口罩主要是防止傳染他人及阻擋飛沫。他自言由SARS至今，每個病人來訪前後他都會洗手，現時更會帶備酒精搓手液隨時搓手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200304/s00001/1583312309626/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B8%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%B2%E7%84%A1%E5%89%8D%E4%BE%8B%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E9%9B%96%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%AC%86%E6%87%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200304%2Fs00001%2F1583312309626%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%259B%2596%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BD%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%25AC%2586%25E6%2587%2588&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=251f4cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200304%2Fs00001%2F1583312309626%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%259B%2596%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BD%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%25AC%2586%25E6%2587%2588&h=455f9913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200304/s00001/1583312309626/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B8%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%B2%E7%84%A1%E5%89%8D%E4%BE%8B%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E9%9B%96%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%AC%86%E6%87%88</a>"},{"pid":"fcf201fd601333de92e575c72775549a52c96d2d","tid":1909920,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"邊班專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c215da8dba3e0dccad583129e9efeb0451018f","tid":1909920,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲專家食屎啦.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>大家快啲上Twitter幫手！</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運動未完架！只係你唔夠投入！</span></strong><br />\n去 tg <span style=\"color: green;\">@TwitterHelpBot</span> 入<span style=\"color: green;\"> /task2</span> 拎任務<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">RT + LIKE + COMMENT</span></span><br />\n多你一個好多！"},{"pid":"e9d90bede4f9fa9dbe62367ed6dc4f1d66c278d8","tid":1909920,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,